{"tid":2100750,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"中共派錢比你移民, 請把握最後的大牛市","createTime":"2020-07-09T09:30:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-13T07:04:30.000Z","uid":76310,"like":160,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"da83cba1ba1c7973f6fd9634379114fd9b9a9830","tid":2100750,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T09:30:07.000Z","msg":"為左落西方社會面, 證明實行国安法後, 一切如常<br />\n甚至比之前更好, 4萬點不是夢<br />\n把握最後大牛市, 搵夠移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能大家會問, 咁要買什麼?<br />\n港版納指: 阿里巴巴, 騰訊, 美團點評, 京東, 網易, 小米集團, 閱文, 微盟集團, 中芯國際等<br />\n強国傾全国全力, 做靚個市比西方社會睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />執唔執, 你地自己諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c8518c1bd1ce58884bae9f6d486d533b56d7305","tid":2100750,"uid":76310,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T09:31:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abb2408d4ec263f27f73657ffc78a9f697136d69","tid":2100750,"uid":141060,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T09:32:57.000Z","msg":"係要燈 屌"},{"pid":"64a773221c780aa116ab803aeae823078697c2d1","tid":2100750,"uid":76310,"like":15,"dislike":3,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T09:34:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n保守估計, 強国起碼掉過萬億黎炒高個市<br />\n營造美麗畫面<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aafe73931885acc9e186b